<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-214] add new &quot;stat reset&quot; command to server admin port</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-214</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A new command should be added to the server admin port (client port) that allows users to reset the stats.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We saw cases during troubleshooting where we would have liked to reset the &quot;min/avg/max latency&quot; stats, but were unable to do so (short of restarting the server).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12407819">ZOOKEEPER-214</key>
            <summary>add new &quot;stat reset&quot; command to server admin port</summary>
